{"type": "article", "id": 28422, "title": "多功能家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-20T06:55:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145544mfWTMhdQtJ8xbEZH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>设计师<a href=\"http://www.designforindustry.jp/\">北川大輔</a>最近为日本品牌 time&amp;style 设计了一款多功能家具 Trifle。Trifle 是一个圆柱形的容器，两侧设有开口同时也可以作为手柄使用。由一块 1.2 毫米厚度的钢片加工制作而成，在满足结构强度的同时保证了它轻盈如纸的重量，简洁的造型使它适用于各种空间。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145541U29dtCMaXgn6OlPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145542Uofgpx4bOhkQXvt1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021455425zh3NE9JlM8sTfIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145543KrgjfaBOSDnFdHI3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}